prisma_schema:
datasource db {
  provider = "mongodb"
  url      = "mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster0.uvkwxgc.mongodb.net/TweetsCollection"
}

model tweets {
  id          String   @id @default(auto()) @map("_id") @db.ObjectId
  avatar      String
  date        DateTime @db.Date
  displayName String
  image       String?
  text        String
  username    String
  verified    Boolean
}
